{
  "stem": "11722.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "I remember my mother threw a sheet down, and we threw stuff into the sheet.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] people holding on to their loved ones.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And we were in the middle of the street with blood strewn all over. | remember going through the streets to watch the brick factory, and non-Jews looking out the window, some people we knew, and nobody lifted a finger to help us.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "I remember the pious Jews praying, you know, the [YIDDISH], the redemption will come.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "God will help.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "I remember at the time I sort of lost faith in God for the time being.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "Our destination was to a brick factory where the setting was just right.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "They had these sheds, long sheds, where they dried the bricks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And there was our housing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS] We had to do calisthenics.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "My father had to go out in the middle of the brick factory.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "They had to do all kinds of heavy calisthenics without their hat on.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "My father was completely bald.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "After a couple days, my father's eyes were puffed from sunstroke.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I felt sorry for my dad.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "He couldn't do anything for the family.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "They didn't feed us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "We had to carry brick from one end of the factory to the other for no reason whatsoever, just to torture us.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "They didn't feed us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "And the setting was so where they had these railroad tracks come in, and they backed in these freight cars, these cattle cars.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "And I remember people actually were packing up and they were standing in line to go, because they probably thought nothing can be as bad as we have it in the brick factory.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So people lined up.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And slowly, slowly they are emptying the brick factory.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
